{
  "texts": [
    "In Sect. 2, we provide an Overview of the Digital Services Act and its categorization of online entities.",
    "Within, Sect. 2.2 elucidates the provisions on AI accountability.",
    "Critiques of the DSA's approach towards disinformation are articulated in Sect. 3, encompassing an analysis of the DSA's regulatory antecedents Sect.",
    "3.1 and leading to a review of the DSA's persistent gaps in Sect. 3.2.",
    "The latter section encompasses legal, technical, psychological, behavioral, and ethical critiques."
  ]
}